module REQ_EXAM_SCHED_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-EXAM-SCHED-01
 * Title       : Schedule Exams with Date Range and Optional Time Limit
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
